"title": "4811: darkness, as a symbol of sin",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "4811",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Darkness is often used in Scripture as a symbol of sin and its effects. It is often contrasted with light, as a symbol of forgiveness and the presence of God.</p>\n<h2>Darkness as a symbol of sin</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:19-John3:20\">JHN 3:19–3:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job24:16-Job24:17\">JOB 24:16–24:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov2:12-Prov2:15\">PRO 2:12–2:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov4:19\">PRO 4:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa5:20\">ISA 5:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa29:15\">ISA 29:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:23\">MAT 6:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke22:53\">LUK 22:53</a> <em>Jesus Christ arrested</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:21\">ROM 1:21</a>ROM <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom13:12\">13:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor6:14\">2CO 6:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:8-Eph5:12\">EPH 5:8–5:12</a>\n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John1:5-1John1:6\">1JN 1:5–1:6</a></p>\n<h2>Darkness as a symbol of the effects of sin</h2>\n<h3>Darkness symbolising ignorance of the truth</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor4:4\">2CO 4:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps82:5\">PSA 82:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa8:20\">ISA 8:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor3:14-2Cor3:15\">2CO 3:14–3:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:18\">EPH 4:18</a></p>\n<h3>Darkness symbolising the inability to find the right way</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:35\">JHN 12:35</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job12:24-Job12:25\">JOB 12:24–12:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa59:9-Isa59:10\">ISA 59:9–59:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:14\">MAT 5:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:9\">1JN 2:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:11\">1JN 2:11</a></p>\n<h3>Darkness symbolises times of trial</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job3:3-Job3:6\">JOB 3:3–3:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job19:8\">JOB 19:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job23:16-Job23:17\">JOB 23:16–23:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job30:26\">JOB 30:26</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps107:10\">PSA 107:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps143:3\">PSA 143:3</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl11:8\">ECC 11:8</a></p>\n<h3>Darkness symbolises death and the grave</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job10:20-Job10:22\">JOB 10:20–10:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps49:19\">PSA 49:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps88:10-Ps88:12\">PSA 88:10–88:12</a></p>\n<h2>God's provision for the darkness of sin</h2>\n<h3>God himself is a remedy for darkness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam22:29\">2SA 22:29</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps18:28\">PSA 18:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps30:5\">PSA 30:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps91:4-Ps91:7\">PSA 91:4–91:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa42:16\">ISA 42:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa50:10\">ISA 50:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic7:8\">MIC 7:8</a></p>\n<h3>God will deliver from darkness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa9:2\">ISA 9:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt4:16\">MAT 4:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps107:13-Ps107:14\">PSA 107:13–107:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa29:18\">ISA 29:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa49:8-Isa49:9\">ISA 49:8–49:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:78-Luke1:79\">LUK 1:78–1:79</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts26:17-Acts26:18\">ACT 26:17–26:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:13\">COL 1:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess5:4-1Thess5:5\">1TH 5:4–5:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:9\">1PE 2:9</a></p>\n<h3>God's Son saves believers from darkness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:12\">JHN 8:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:4-John1:5\">JHN 1:4–1:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:46\">JHN 12:46</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor4:5\">1CO 4:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor4:6\">2CO 4:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:3\">GEN 1:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:8\">EPH 5:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet1:19\">2PE 1:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:8\">1JN 2:8</a></p>\n<h3>God's people rescue others from darkness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa42:6-Isa42:7\">ISA 42:6–42:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa60:1-Isa60:5\">ISA 60:1–60:5</a></p>",
